# PEEK context maps land here

This directory is populated by `promoteContextMapCandidate` Cloud Function (Phase PEEK.1).
Each promoted map lives at `harness/context-maps/{recipeID}.json` mirroring
`harness/context-recipes/{recipeID}.json` filename 1:1.

Files in this directory are written by Cloud Function automation only. Do not hand-edit
unless reverting a bad promotion (which the admin UI lacks for PEEK.1 - `git revert`
the offending commit).

ASCII-only contents required: Swift decoder rejects non-ASCII in JSON files it reads
(memory `gotchas_swift_decoder_non_ascii_strings.md`).
